description: With the motto of Hands to Hearts, Lakshyam works to safeguard and uplift children of not so privileged sections of the society. One of such is Vasant Kunj's Sindhi Basti where 11 months ago Lakshyam NGO had set-up its school and camp for the betterment of children and people living in that area. This area is inhabited by around 100 families and approx 300 children who are seen begging or selling toys or performing on tarffic signals or are rag-pickers.
Address: Lakhsyam Center, Sindhi Basti E 2 Block Vasant Kunj, New Delhi, India
Time: Sat Nov 18 2017 at 10:00 am to Sat Nov 25 2017 at 06:00 pm
